data.description: This is an amazing 1 story home with an incredible price!  Fabulous neighborhood with community pool and playground! Smith Elementary has an A rating!Carpet replaced in the bedrooms, wood look laminate in the family room, and interior painted.Looks gorgeous and is ready for a new owner.The kitchen is a fabulous size with plenty of counter space for food prep and tons of storage.The breakfast bar is perfect for additional seating or a great place to work.A large dining space is just off the kitchen and can accommodate a large table. The family room is spacious and open to the kitchen and dining space making it ideal for entertaining.You will love how the bedrooms are split for privacy.Primary bedroom is nicely tucked at the rear of the home and has a great ensuite bathroom with huge walk-in closet.The secondary bedrooms are on another wing of the home and have great closets and ceiling fans.This is a great floor plan! Outside is a huge yard!
